    Aliment Pharmacol Ther
    Colorectal cancer in elderly-onset inflammatory bowel disease: A 1969-2017 Scandinavian register-based cohort study.
 The excess risk of CRC in elderly-onset IBD was probably due to bias and not observed beyond the first year. From 2010, the HR for CRC diagnosis more than 1year after initial IBD diagnosis was lower than in the largely unscreened reference population, supporting the benefit of endoscopic screening and surveillance in patients with IBD.
