    Automatic Captioning of Early Gastric Cancer via Magnification Endoscopy with Narrow Band Imaging.
 EGCCap exhibited promising captioning performance and was proved with satisfying generalization, robustness, and interpretability. Our study showed potential value in aiding and improving the diagnosis of EGC and facilitating the development of automated reporting in the future.
